ultimately have "LS=LT" using subspace_dim_equal[of LS LT] ls lt by auto
moreover have "S = {x. ? y : LS. a+y=x}" using LS_def by auto 
moreover have "T = {x. ? y : LT. a+y=x}" using LT_def by auto
ultimately show ?thesis by auto 
